  "title": "Learning & Development ( L&D ) Senior Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client, a well-established organisation is seeking for a Learning & Development ( L&D ) Senior Manager - $ 8,500.00 + AWS + attractive Bonuses / 21 annual leave / CentralWest Area</strong><br /></p><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Degree in Human Resources Management or Business or relevant. </li><li><strong>At least 10 years of full spectrum of L&D experience, with at least 5 years in a senior role </strong></li><li><strong>Strong leadership and supervisory skills.</strong></li><li><strong>Strong communication and writing skill</strong></li><li><strong>Experience in working with Senior Management/HOD to develop the appropriate learning and development strategies.</strong></li><li><strong>Experience in transformation projects leading to excellence in organisation culture or Learning & Development or HR practices</strong></li><li><strong>Familiar with Skills Future and other Sectoral Competency Frameworks to identify growth areas for company employees</strong></li></ul><p>Others</p><ul><li>Salary up to $ 8,500.00 + AWS + attractive bonuses</li><li>21 annual leave</li><li>CentralWest Area</li><li>Walking distance from MRT station</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested candidate can send in your resume (word format prefer) to <strong>grayson.su@thetalentnetwork.com.sg</strong></p>",
